You could move the code within run() into a private method and then call the scheduler with this method:
websocketpollingjob = scheduler.scheduleWithFixedDelay(this::myNewMethod, 0, 30, TimeUnit.SECONDS);
That avoids the boiler plate code of defining an anonymous class.

